results.title: When Strikes A Gladiator!
results.description: Cannonball and Gladiator go toe-to-toe; Gladiator transports the X-Men out to save the Shi'ar Empire.

results.title: Where No X-Man Has Gone Before!
Casualties of War
results.description: The X-Men try to save the Shi'ar homeworld from the Phalanx; Kelly and Gyrich realize what a monster Operation Zero Tolerance has become.

results.title: With The X-Men Missing... Marrow Goes Wild!
Gambit's Greatest Secret Revealed...And Some Sins Can Never Be Forgiven !
Trial & Errors
results.description: Erik reveals to the captured X-Men that Gambit gathered the Marauders for Sinister to initiate the Mutant Massacre.

results.title: Welcome to the X-Men Cecilia...You Know The Rest!
Hours & Minutes
results.description: Cecilia leaves the X-Men to continue work at the hospital, but now that all of her collegues know she is a mutant, she is forced to put up with prejudice; Pyro comes into the hospital and she treats him but he makes off while she is tending another superhero, Daredevil; Cecilia is fired and she returns to X-Mansion.

results.title: Who Art They? What Are They ?
Thieves In The Temple
results.description: Black Tom contacts Storm and asks for her aid in re-taking the Gem of Cytorrak to heal a dying Juggernaut; Storm agrees and is joined by the missing Gambit who decides to return to the X-Men once their mission is complete.

results.title: Meltdown (The Hunt For Xavier Part One)
results.description: The X-Men try to contain a crazed and extremely powerful Pyro who is dying from the Legacy Virus; Clues from Pyro put the team on the trail of their missing mentor.

results.title: When You're Unwanted (The Hunt For Xavier Part Three)
results.description: The hunt for Xavier leads the X-Men to Alcatraz where they run up against a new brotherhood of mutants trained by Charlie himself; Xavier reveals that the enemy is the sentient Cerebro.

results.title: Escape From Alcatraz (The Hunt For Xavier Part Five)
results.description: The X-Men defeat one of Cerebro's aspects, but the battle is far from over.

results.title: The Shot Heard Round The World (The Magneto War Part One)
results.description: The Acolytes lead the X-Men on a wild goose chase while Magneto begins his war for peace on all of humanity; Sabra discovers that Joseph is a copy of Magneto

results.title: The Magneto War Part 3: Unholy Trinity
Disturbing Behavior (The Magneto War Part Three)
results.description: The X-Men continue their battle with the Acolytes; Astra uses Joseph to try and take down Magneto.

results.title: The War Is Over--But Payback Has Just Begun !
Mansions In Heaven
results.description: The X-Men have a funeral for Joseph; Wolvie tries to figure out how to invade Genosha and take Maggie down.

results.title: Collision Course
results.description: The X-Men face down an interdimensional Juggernaut.

results.title: History Repeats
results.description: The X-Men try desperately to warn the Skrulls about the coming of Galactus while Gambit tries desperately to get Marrow some medical attention.

results.title: The Dawn of M-Tech: Warlock Enslaved
Rage Against the Machine Part 1: Crossed Wires
results.description: Shield captures Machine Man and uses his technology to help build their new Deathlok; The X-Men land their Skrull ship at Muir Island where a few of them stay behind to recoup.

results.title: Dream's End Chapter One: Rude Awakening
results.description: With barely a breath since their last adventure, Xavier begins training the X-Men into the ground.

results.title: Beauty & The Beast Part One: Broken Mirrors
results.description: Pete and Marrow are in Boston taking time off from the X-Men when Mikhail pulls them into his dimension.

results.title: Team Shattered--Trapped On a World Gone Mad !
Beauty & The Beast Part 2: You Can't Go Home Again
results.description: Colossus and Marrow fight to keep Mikhail from resurrecting a false image of Illyana; Mikhail is purged of an evil entity and all three return to earth.

results.title: I Am Not Now, Nor Have I Ever Been...
results.description: Xavier sends the X-Men on a wild mind trip pitting teammate against teammate to find out where all loyalties lie; The recently deceased Wolverine is really a skrull (and has been since X-Men #90).
